<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10301518>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1A–J. Otoniela adisi Brescovit, 1997.Male (IBSP 29715; 58258):A habitus, dorsal view; C Cephalothorax, chelicerae, dorsal view (arrow indicate fang base with protuberance); D left palp expanded, prolateral view; E left palp expanded, retrolateral view; F left palp, ventral view; G left palp, prolateral view; H left palp, retrolateral view; I left palp, retrodorsal view. Female (IBSP 11452): B habitus, dorsal view; J Epigynum, ventral view. Abbreviations:A, atrium; EBA, embolar base apophysis; BH, basal haematodocha; CO, copulatory opening; C, cymbium; DPA, dorsal patellar apophysis; E, embolus; LB, lateral borders; MA, median apophysis; P, petiole; RTA, retrolateral tibial apophysis; PTA, prolateral tibial apophysis; RPA, retrolateral patellar apophysis; ST, subtegulum; T, tegulum; VTP, ventral tegular projection. Scale bars: A, B 2.16mm; C 0.83mm; D, E, F, J 0.25mm; G–I 0.5mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10301518/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10301522>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2A–L. Otoniela adisi Brescovit, 1997. Male (IBSP 11452): A chelicera, ventral view; B chelicera, paturon (detail, arrow indicate fang base with protuberance); C colulus, ventral view; D anterior lateral spinneret; E posterior median spinneret; F posterior lateral spinneret; G leg I, femur in ventral view (arrows indicate the spines); H claws, tarsus I, retrolateral view; I claws, tarsus IV, prolateral view; J tricobothrium, dorsal view; K tarsal organ, dorsal view; L slit sensilla, dorsal view. Abbreviations: Ac, aciniform gland spigot; CL, colulus; MaAm, major ampullate gland spigot; MiAm, minor ampullate gland spigot; Pi, piriform gland spigot. Scale bars: A 0.4mm; B 0.3mm(0.04mm); C, D, F, G, H, I 0.5mm; E 0.04mm; J 0.01mm; K, L 0.005mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10301522/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10301528>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3A–L. Otoniela adisi Brescovit, 1997. Male (IBSP 11452):A left palp, ventral view; B same, prolateral view; C same, ventral view; D same, retrolateral view (arrows indicate lyriform organ in the patella); E left palp, patella, retrolateral view (arrows indicate the lyriform organ in the patella); F left palp, dorsal view; G left palp, copulatory bulb, ventral view (arrow indicate the denticle in the median apophysis); H same, ventral view; I same, retroventral view (arrow indicate the denticle in the median apophysis). Female (IBSP 11454): J vulva, dorsal view; K same, zoom in spermatheca, dorsal view; L vulva, details spermatheca, dorsal view. Abbreviations: EBA, embolar base apophysis; BG, Bennett’s gland, CD, copulatory ducts; DPA, dorsal patellar apophysis; E, embolus; FD, fertilization ducts; GD, gland ducts; MA, median apophysis; PTA, prolateral tibial apophysis; RTA, retrolateral tibial apophysis; RPA, retrolateral patellar apophysis; S, spermathecae; SR, seminal receptacles; ST, subtegulum; T, tegulum; VTP, ventral tegular projection. Scale bars: A 0.4mm; B, G, J 0.2mm; C, D, F, H, I, K 0.01mm; E 0.05mm; L 0.03mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10301528/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10301530>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4A–H. Otoniela lupercioi sp. nov.. Male (IBSP 29716): A habitus, dorsal view; C, D left palp, ventral view; E same, prolateral view; F same, retrolateral view. Female (IBSP 29715): B habitus, dorsal view; G epigynum, ventral view; H vulva, dorsal view. Abbreviations: A, atrium; EBA, embolar basal apophysis; CD, copulatory ducts; DPA, dorsal patellar apophysis; E, embolus; FD, fertilization ducts; LB, lateral borders; MA, median apophysis; PTA, prolateral tibial apophysis; RTA, retrolateral tibial apophysis; RPA, retrolateral patellar apophysis; S, spermatheca; ST, subtegulum, T, tegulum, VTP, ventral tegular projection. Scale bars: A 2.6mm; B 3.5mm; C, F, G 0.25mm; D, E 0.5mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10301530/files/figure.png" ;
